-- MOVES-BDO hires Steffan Adfeldt from Barclays as tax director
-- By Anet Josline Pinto in Bangalore
-- Tue Oct 14, 2014 07:43AM EDT
-- None



Oct 14 (Reuters) - BDO LLP, an accountancy and business advisory firm, said it hired Steffan Adfeldt from Barclays Plc <BARC.L> to join as a tax director in its financial services group.

At Barclays, Adfeldt oversaw all tax aspects of treasury matters at group level, including funding, hedging and prudential regulatory reform, BDO said in a statement.